{"tid":671032,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美聯樓價最新報169.67點 按周升0.57%","createTime":"2018-05-19T19:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T00:47:57.000Z","uid":68476,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"78c4322176795306368f056a6d806212954d81b5","tid":671032,"uid":68476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T19:20:00.000Z","msg":"美聯樓價最新報169.67點 按周升0.57%<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://plib.aastocks.com/aafnnews/image/medialib/20180508141736726_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplib.aastocks.com%2Faafnnews%2Fimage%2Fmedialib%2F20180508141736726_l.jpg&h=bef84ac5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美聯樓價指數最新(5月9日至5月15日)報169.67點，按周續升約0.57%，樓價續創歷史新高；指數較四星期前升約1.63%；年內迄今亦已累升約8.05%。<br />\n<br />\n當中，美聯港島樓價指數升幅最大，按周升約1.04%至188.2點；美聯新界樓價指數最新報159.45點，按周升約0.8%；而美聯九龍樓價指數最新報160.58點，按周回落約0.77%。"},{"pid":"dfa2fdedc089d8f272306488771d06c12e8cecbf","tid":671032,"uid":46910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T19:36:25.000Z","msg":"升到世界末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed00ab39278dfa3437f22dad36b9cf41d42f70f7","tid":671032,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T19:37:08.000Z","msg":"升到十萬蚊一呎先合理嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> UPUPUP"},{"pid":"3a2ba0c1122ed86f01cc4b36e38168cf243690bf","tid":671032,"uid":30427,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T23:47:58.000Z","msg":"低過中原指數，係唔係同美聯買樓會抵d？"},{"pid":"3ac17ea133ccfe8617d21e699fd14725987e1e1b","tid":671032,"uid":67655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T00:10:02.000Z","msg":"樓市痴線 一直升<br />\n仲癲過股市"},{"pid":"17fb1ef70a5803404a2fb51b2c36ce681c28df5e","tid":671032,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T00:43:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5677cded5d2a4ea5768ebda03159c2